</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Problematično područje
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P0137: Niski napon kruga O2 senzora
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Kada je napon HO2S signala niži od 0,06 V, napon kruga HO2S signala ne mijenja se tijekom 5 s uz primjenu napona na krug HO2S signala.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(logika detekcije 3 ciklusa vožnje)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" morerows = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
HO2S i/ili njegov krug
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
HO2S grijač i/ili njegov krug
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Ispušni sustav
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Sustav usisa zraka
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Sustav goriva
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ECM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P0138: Visoki napon kruga O2 senzora
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Izlazni napon kruga signala HO2S veći je od 1,1 V tijekom 5 s.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(logika detekcije 3 ciklusa vožnje)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P0140: Nije detektirana aktivnost strujnog kruga O2 senzora
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Bilo koji od sljedećih uvjeta je ispunjen. 
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Strujni krug HO2S signala je prekinut.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Unutarnji otpor HO2S-a viši je od propisanog, čak iako je procijenjena temperatura ispušnih plinova viša od propisane.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<ptxt>
(logika detekcije 3 ciklusa vožnje)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</servinfosub>
